      "span_text": "The mass spectrometry proteomics data have been deposited to the ProteomeXchange Consortium (http://proteomecentral.proteomexchange.org) via the iProX partner repository [CITATION_1] with the dataset identifier PXD014363, the subject ID is IPX0001646002."
